data.value:
Tequila sunrise, a small amount of tequila produced in Mexico, mixed with a large amount of fresh orange juice and brown sugar water. Decorated with orange corners or red cherries, a tall champagne glass will give it an elegant look. The name is the same as the music composed by Igorus.
Base wine: Tequila Ingredients: Orange juice Lemon juice Pomegranate juice Price: £4
